item.description:
As always I will be going to Bar on Crown street for my birthday for "dancing"! At least thats what I like to call what my crazy flailing around on the dance floor. So if you like loud music, group dancing, and cheep drinks or if you just like birthdays, come down and hang for the night. I will be there definatly by 10p. I may be there earlier for dinner, I will update as we get closer.
*This meetup is not exclusive to our group, I may have some co-workers and friends attending.
item.how_to_find_us: In the back bar area, dance floor. 203.499.7299
item.name: As Aways Dancing! AT BAR
